item.description:
Daft Punk - Random Access Memories (Drumless Edition) [Fan-Made]
16bit - 48kHz
Daft Punk recently announced the upcoming release of Drumless Edition for Random Access Memories
While us fans wait, you can take a listen to this fan-made version made from the 22.2ch Sony 360 Reality Audio release of RAM.
It should be noted that no AI has been used so some tracks might lack what should be found on the official release from Daft Punk
